  "title": "Marketing Trainee (Entry level)",
  "description": "<p> Marketing Trainee (Structured Career Growth)<br /></p><p>Join a leading global sales & marketing organization representing well-known brands. We're <br />looking for driven individuals - including mid-career switcher - who enjoy connecting with people and want a clear pathway to advancement. <br /></p><p>What You Will Do</p><ul><li>Represent clients professionally through face-to-face engagement </li><li>Build strong customer relationships </li><li>Contribute to brand growth and customer experience </li></ul><p><br />What We Offer </p><ul><li>Weekly payouts with performance incentives </li><li>Structured training and 1-1 coaching </li><li>Clear career progression into leadership roles </li><li>Supportive, collaborative team environment </li></ul><p>Who Thrives Here </p><ul><li>Individuals with strong communication skills </li><li>People who enjoy continuous learning </li><li>Candidates seeking career growth, regardless of previous experience </li></ul>",
